quran[58]{c,v,t}:
  37,145,Koma Ife tidakamuponya pa mtunda pamene iye anali kudwala
  37,146,Ndipo Ife tidameretsa chitsamba cha chipanda kuti chimere pamwamba pake
  37,147,Ndipo tidamutumiza kwa anthu zikwi makumi khumi kapena kuposa apa
  37,148,Ndipo onse adakhulupirira ndipo Ife tidawapatsa chisangalalo cha kanthawi kochepa
  37,149,"Ndipo tsopano afunseni kuti, “Kodi Ambuye wako ali ndi ana"
  37,150,Kapena kuti Ife tidalenga angelo kukhala akazi pamene iwo anali kuona
  37,151,Kodi iwo sanena zabodza pamene amati
  37,152,“Mulungu wabereka mwana?” Ndithudi iwo ndi abodza
  37,153,Kodi iye adasankha ana aakazi m’malo mwa ana aamuna
  37,154,Kodi mwatani? Kodi mumaweruza bwanji
  37,155,Kodi simungaganize bwino
  37,156,Kapena kodi inu muli ndi ulamuliro weniweni
  37,157,Kotero bweretsani Buku lanu ngati ndinu olungama
  37,158,Ndipo iwo akhazikitsa ubale pakati pa Mulungu ndi majini. Koma majini amadziwa kuti iwo adzatengedwa kupita kwa Iye
  37,159,Ulemerero ukhale kwa Mulungu. Iye ali pamwamba pa zimene amamuyerekeza nazo
  37,160,"Kupatula akapolo a Mulungu, amene Iye amasankha"
  37,161,Ndithudi inu pamodzi ndi zimene mupembedza
  37,162,Simungathe kusocheza wina aliyense
  37,163,Kupatula okhawo amene adzapita ku moto wa ku Gahena
  37,164,Aliyense wa Ife ali ndi malo ake ake
  37,165,Ndithudi ndife amene timaima pa mizere kupemphera
  37,166,"Ndipo, ndithudi, ndife amene timamulemekeza"
  37,167,"Ndipo,\tndithudi,\tiwo\tanali\tkunena\tkuti"
  37,168,“Tikadakhala ndi chikumbutso monga chomwe chinali ndi anthu akale.”
  37,169,"“Ife, ndithudi, tidakhala akapolo osankhidwa a Mulungu.”"
  37,170,Koma iwo sakhulupilira mu izi komabe iwo adzadziwa
  37,171,Ndithudi mawu athu adatsogola kwa akapolo athu omwe ndi Atumwi athu
  37,172,"Kuti iwo, ndithudi, adzathandizidwa"
  37,173,"Ndipo, ndithudi, gulu lathu lokha lidzakhala lopambana"
  37,174,Kotero uyambe wawasiya okha kwa kanthawi kochepa
  37,175,Ndipo uwaone ndipo iwo adzadzioneranso
  37,176,Kodi iwo afuna kufulumizitsa chilango chathu
  37,177,"Koma pamene icho chidzadza pa iwo, udzakhala m’mawa woipa kwa iwo amene adachenjezedwa"
  37,178,Kotero uyambe wawasiya okha kwa kanthawi kochepa
  37,179,Ndipo uwaone ndipo nawo adzaona
  37,180,"Ulemerero ukhale kwa Ambuye wako, Ambuye wolemekezeka ndi wamphamvu, kuposa zimene ali kumukundikira"
  37,181,Ndipo mtendere ukhale kwa Atumwi onse
  37,182,"Ndipo kuyamikidwa ndi kuthokoza konse kukhale kwa Mulungu, Ambuye wa zolengedwa zonse"
  38,1,Suad. Pali Korani yodzadza ndi chikumbutso
  38,2,Iyayi! anthu osakhulupirira ali kungodzikundikira ndi kumangotsutsa
  38,3,Kodi ndi mibadwo ingati imene Ife tidaononga iwo asanadze ndipo iyo idalira poona kuti padalibe nthawi yothawa
  38,4,"Ndipo iwo ali kudabwa kuti Mtumwi wadza kwa iwo kuchokera pakati pawo. Ndipo anthu osakhulupirira amati, “Uyu ndi munthu wamatsenga ndiponso wabodza!”"
  38,5,“Kodi iye wapanga milungu yonse kukhala Mulungu mmodzi? Ndithudi ichi ndi chinthu chachilendo.”
  38,6,"Ndipo atsogoleri awo amachoka monyinyirika nati, “Pitirizani inu ndipo mudzipereke kwathunthu kwa milungu yanu! Ndithudi ichi ndi chinthu choti chikusokonezani.”"
  38,7,“Ife sitidamvepo zimenezi pakati pa anthu akale. Ichi si china koma nkhani zopeka chabe.”
  38,8,“Kodi uthenga wavumbulutsidwa kwa iye yekha pakati pathu?” Iyayi! Koma iwo ali kukayika za uthenga wanga. Iyayi! Iwo sadalawepo chilango changa
  38,9,"Kapena iwo ndi nkhokwe za chifundo cha Ambuye wako, Mwini Mphamvu zonse, Mwini kupereka zabwino zonse"
  38,10,"Kapena iwo ali ndi ulamuliro kumwamba ndi padziko ndi kuti zonse zimene zili m’menemo ndi zawo? Ngati nditero, alekeni iwo kuti akwere mothandizidwa"
  38,11,Iwo adzagonjetsedwa monga magulu akale
  38,12,"Asanadze iwo, panali ena amene adakana Atumwi. Anthu a Nowa, a Aad, ndi a Farawo, mfumu ya zisonga"
  38,13,"Thamoud ndi anthu a Loti ndi anthu okhala m’nkhalango, onsewa adali wothandizana"
  38,14,"Panalibe mmodzi amene sadanene kuti Atumwi adali abodza, motero chilango changa chinali chowayenera"
  38,15,Ndipo awa ali kungodikira kulira kumodzi kokha kumene kuchitike mosachedwa
  38,16,"Iwo amati, “Ambuye wathu, bweretsani msanga kwa ife Buku la ntchito zathu ngakhale nthawi yake siinakwane.”"
  38,17,"Khala wopirira pa zimene ali kunena ndipo uzikumbukira kapolo wathu Davide, munthu wamphamvu. Ndithudi iye anali kulapa nthawi zonse"
  38,18,Ndithudi Ife tidauza mapiri kuti aziyimba pamodzi ndi iye mayamiko athu nthawi ya madzulo ndi m’mbandakucha
  38,19,"Ndipo mbalame zidasonkhana, zonse pamodzi ndi iye zidalemekeza Mulungu"
  38,20,Tidalimbikitsa Ufumu wake ndipo tidamupatsa nzeru ndi kuweruza kwabwino m’manenedwe ndi m’chiweruzo